    "data": [
        {
            "id": 6008198,
            "title": "亞泥花蓮礦區爆破作業波及民宅 主動停工改善",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>亞泥 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1102:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1102\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1102-TW</a>) 花蓮新城山礦區 4 日進行例行作業時，發生零星小碎石飛出，波及民宅和多功能活動中心屋頂事故，幸未造成任何人員傷亡；亞泥今 (5) 日表示，停止花蓮礦區爆破作業，並再次向受影響居民致歉，並全力處理賠償。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008198%2Fl%2F82e18085ee8d5bc482b266cfdebf172c.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">亞泥董事長徐旭東。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>亞泥表示，高度重視此次事件，為展現負責任態度並讓社區居民安心，已於今日在意外發生地點主動停止爆破作業，後續也將主動與主管機關與地方社區保持密切溝通，確保各項作業符合最高安全標準，在完成改善措施後才會復工。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>對於受影響居民的部分，亞泥說明，第一時間立即派員說明，致上誠摯歉意，並致贈慰問金外，也協助修繕受損部分，目前民宅修復作業已完成，活動中心因屬於高空作業，目前積極處裡中，會以最快速度，完成修復。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>亞泥強調，已啟動全面檢討機制，針對作業各環節強化控管措施，同時提升現場監督密度與作業人員教育訓練，全面提升施工安全標準，將社區安全與居民福祉視為企業營運根本，將持續以更加嚴謹的態度落實風險管理與作業監督，強化安全防線，杜絕相同事件發生。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
