        {
            "id": 6008247,
            "title": "信紘科每股配8.55元現金股利 殖利率4.34%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>信紘科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6667:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6667\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6667-TW</a>) 今 (5) 日舉辦股東會，決議通過每股現金股利<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a> 8.55 元之盈餘分配案，配發率 88.24%、近 9 成，依今日收盤價格 197 元計算，現金殖利率約 4.34%，凸顯全體經營階層努力不懈，將整體營運成果資訊與全體股東共享。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008247%2Fl%2Fa8e22e177d43fd72cbedba458e76bad5.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">左二為信紘科董事長簡士堡、左三為總經理王怡文。(圖：信紘科提供)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>信紘科股東會今日由董事長簡士堡先生主持，會中承認並通過 2024 年度營業報告書及財務報表、盈餘分配案及公司章程修訂等相關討論事項。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>信紘科去年營運寫下新里程碑，2024 年營收達 36.28 億元，年增 50.37%，主要受惠於來自半導體、面板、記憶體等高科技產業客戶持續穩定推進新廠擴建與新增產能計劃，加上台灣內需公共建設需求持續暢旺，營收創下新高。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>信紘科去年稅後淨利達 4.36 億元，較前年同步成長 35.87%，每股稅後盈餘 (EPS) 達 9.69 元，2024 年營收、獲利皆締造歷史新高，2024 年股東權益報酬率 (ROE)、資產報酬率 (ROA) 分別由前一年度的 22.1%、10.35% 提升至 25.67%、11.78%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>信紘科強調，經營團隊戮力深化公司治理，為創造公司、員工與全體股東最大價值不遺餘力。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
